- As a developer, I want to create a new blank Blazor project, so that I’ll have a
basic working environment to start with.
- As a developer, I want to explore and figure out how Blazor’s file structure works,
so that I’ll know how to properly develop with it.
- As a user, I want a basic home page that has some kind of basic text on it, so
that I have a homepage to go to.
- As a user, I want a navigation bar, so that I can move between page 1 and page 2.
- As a user, I want some kind of styling on the home page that is different from
the second page, so that I can tell when I navigate between them.
- As a user, I want the second page to have different text on it from the homepage,
so that I can tell when I navigate between them.
